---
// Argus CRAG pipeline diagram — used on /projects/lawagent
// SVG source lives at /public/argus-pipeline.svg and is mirrored to the
// LawAgent demo at /static/argus-pipeline.svg so both surfaces display
// the identical diagram. Update the SVG in one place, copy to the other.
---

<figure class="pipeline-diagram my-6">
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface p-3 sm:p-5 overflow-x-auto">
    <img
      src="/argus-pipeline.svg"
      alt="Argus Corrective RAG pipeline: anonymize → embed → retrieve from Neon pgvector → rerank → Gemini → branch to Hub artifacts or Chat stream → Supermemory write"
      class="block w-full h-auto"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>
  <figcaption class="text-xs text-muted text-center mt-3 italic">
    Boxes with a double burgundy border are persistent data layers; single-border boxes are compute steps. The
    optional dashed inbound arrow at the pgvector stage is the per-session context read from Supermemory, skipped
    when the session has no uploaded documents.
  </figcaption>
</figure>
